{"tid":740490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【隱世部落】與世隔絕5萬年僅剩400人 政府開發公路族人恐10年內消失","createTime":"2018-07-13T02:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T04:47:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"18c47d6ed045d37ce30fb46f0647731ad288526a","tid":740490,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180712/large/1531375260_6852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180712%2Flarge%2F1531375260_6852.jpg&h=c1137afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度洋群島上一個原始部落面臨威脅，他們曾經與世隔絕5.5萬年，目前族人只剩400人，由於印度政府開發公路，令觀光客和盜獵者湧入，有保護組織擔心這些族人可能在10年內就會消失。<br />\n<br />\n這個隱世部落稱為加洛瓦（Jarawa）族群，居於印度洋安達曼群島（Andaman islands）上，他們是遊牧民族，自給自足，懂得用特製的「加洛瓦弓」，狩獵豬、蜥蜴和龜等動物，以及捕漁維生。他們對島上逾150種植物和350種動物都瞭如指掌，除了食用果實外，還會利用草藥令蜜蜂鎮靜下來，取得蜂蜜。<br />\n<br />\n但當局開發了一條橫越加洛瓦人家園的高速公路，令外界入侵他們的生活，慈善組織「生存國際」(Survival International)表示，遊客到訪村落對待村民「有如參觀動物園」；另外還有盜獵者闖入當地原始森林打獵，影響加洛瓦人的食物來源－－他們主要靠打獵維生。種種原因，令加洛瓦人敵視外來者。<br />\n<br />\n有關心事件的人士發起網上聯署「加洛瓦運動」，希望保護這個原始部落，目前已有約25萬人參與。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加洛瓦人安然度過英國和日本殖民時期，不受外界打擾，但當地政府卻在1990年決定發展大計，將加洛瓦人重置在兩個村落，以發展捕漁業，甚至想規定族人的衣著，幸好在多個團體請願後，這個計劃在2000年時擱置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180713/58431871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180713%2F58431871&d=HEH8e4qRqfSiWwmKscOQDC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=cb339d3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180713%2F58431871&h=2ca58df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180713/58431871</a>"},{"pid":"e5c302feb4a0bb067477e72a72e8600411edc7dc","tid":740490,"uid":183178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"唔知有無隱世美食"},{"pid":"c9a9d3a172e17e88b3ac489d1744a9b221f5e444","tid":740490,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"搬哂入博物館囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff828b65ce24e58e08bb7e27f2dc745ed58fb2d","tid":740490,"uid":111253,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:36:55.000Z","msg":"WAKANDA FOREVER"},{"pid":"494f51f1f094e09db4f773e9574a88ec560ca894","tid":740490,"uid":49208,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"好天真無邪既一雙眼<br />\n希望佢地未來唔需要返工"},{"pid":"c3d4dee65ddbef3eb350475bafbc2e99e62b45d9","tid":740490,"uid":9286,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"支持佢地殺晒外來入侵者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7aae3f5703d5c86f45af803be9df82e0a2a43d","tid":740490,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a63c04711e02cb5831157ba1bd563f07dc63a77","tid":740490,"uid":9286,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"fb7aae3f5703d5c86f45af803be9df82e0a2a43d","tid":740490,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"c3d4dee65ddbef3eb350475bafbc2e99e62b45d9","tid":740490,"uid":9286,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"支持佢地殺晒外來入侵者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"咁圍村人有冇與世隔絕 冇就收聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9bc9264dbfc5a6a8d7de94a13541fdddd23a47","tid":740490,"uid":102240,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"3a63c04711e02cb5831157ba1bd563f07dc63a77","tid":740490,"uid":9286,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"fb7aae3f5703d5c86f45af803